# 77 Projects App Initialization Guide

## Description

This rule provides a comprehensive checklist and code templates for initializing new Next.js applications following the 77-projects structure. Use this when creating a new project from scratch.

## Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+ installed
- pnpm package manager installed (`npm install -g pnpm`)
- Git installed and configured

